<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She showed some love for her sister's baby daddy Scott Disick on Monday, as she shared a snap from a recent day of filming Keeping Up With The Kardashians.</p>

<p>And after posting the sweet snap with her pal, Kim Kardashian was seen arriving at another friend's house for dinner in Malibu on Monday evening.</p>

<p>The businesswoman, 39, was dressed to impress in a pair of stylish white belted trousers, which showcased her famous peachy posterior. </p>

<p>Arrival: Kim Kardashian was seen arriving at another friend's house for dinner in Malibu on Monday evening</p>

<p>Kim styled the look with a blue sheer top, which she wore over a white top and teamed with a pair of snakeskin print heels, boasting her pint-sized frame.</p>

<p>The mother-of-four worked her glossy raven locks up into a chic up do, and enhanced her striking features with a bronze pallet of make-up.</p>

<p>Forgoing any accessorised, Kim kept the attention on her fashionable ensemble while getting out of her matte black 4x4. </p>

